{
  "stem": "2684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't a definite identification.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Amongst one of the adults who came out, said that this must be [NON-ENGLISH] because his uniform was a very, very-- you could see that he is a very high in the force, which I can't call police force because it was not the police.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a different-- they were the executor for a long way back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm talking about 50 years back in the Hungarian history.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were the police force in the country areas who where doing everything which was not, according to the Hungarians, not just by law, but by definition of the Hungarian way of life.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which means they were anti-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were anti-communist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're anti-socialist.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were anti-poor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were the henchmen of the landlords in Hungary, which landlords we're talking about thousands and thousands of acres per families.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were the executioners of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were feared all over Hungary, not just by the Jews, but by everybody who wasn't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who wasn't wanted by the Hungarian regime.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this guy was very, very high rank.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this man in our wagon said that that must be [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I recognized the man after when I went to the Hungarian Jewish because I was there when Szalasi, who was the head of the fascist movement in Hungary, was trialed and hanged.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was there when Imredy, who was the foreign minister in Hungary, during that time, he was trialed and was hanged.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was there when [NON-ENGLISH] who was the justice minister in the German times, was trialed and hanged.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The way I could go there, my father had a doctor friends who was the jail doctor.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
